    "excerpt": "This is an egalitarian version of the Aneinu litany recited at the end of Seliḥot services, featuring equal representation for the women of the Tanakh and Talmud.  . . .",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nThis is an egalitarian version of the Aneinu litany recited at the end of Seliḥot services, featuring equal representation for the women of the Tanakh and Talmud.</p>\n<p>A recording using one of my favorite melodies can be found <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/isaac-gantwerk-mayer/egalitarian-aneinu-jerusalem-sephardic-melody\">here</a>.\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Transliteration (Romanized Hebrew)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nאֶלֹהֵי אָבוֹתֵֽינוּ<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nGod of our patriarchs!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nElohei avoténu!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nאֶלֹהֵי אַבְרָהָם<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nGod of Abraham!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 28:13&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nElohei Avraham!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nפַּֽחַד יִצְחָק<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nAwe of Isaac!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 31:42&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nPáḥad Yitzḥak!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nאֲבִיר יַעֲקֹב<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nMighty One of Jacob!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 49:26.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nAvir Ya’akov!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nמִשְׂגָב אִמָהוֹת<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nShield of our matriarchs!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nMisgav imahot!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nפּוֹקֵד שָׂרָה<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nAccounting for Sarah!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 21:1&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nPoked Sarah!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nנֶעֱתָּר לְרִבְקָה<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nEntreated One of Rebecca!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Genesis 25:21-22&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nNe’etar l-Rivkah!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nמְנַחֵם רָחֵל<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nComforter of Rachel!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Jeremiah 31:15-16&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nM’naḥem Raḥel!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nשֹׁמֵֽעַ אֶל־לֵאָה<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nListener to Leah!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 30:17&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nShoméa el Leah!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nהָעוֹנֶה בְּעֵת רָצוֹן<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nAnswering in time of need!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nHa-oneh b-et ratzon!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nהָעוֹנֶה בְּעֵת צָרָה<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nAnswering in time of stress!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nHa-oneh b-et tzarah!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nהָעוֹנֶה בְּעֵת רַחֲמִים<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nAnswering in time of mercy!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nHa-oneh b-et raḥamim!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nמָגֵן דָוִד<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nShield of David!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Pesachim 117b&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nMagen David!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nמְקוֹם אֶסְתֵּר<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nPlace of Esther!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Esther 4:14&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nM’kom Esther!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nאֱלָהָא דְּמֵאִיר<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nGod of Meir!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Avodah Zarah 18a&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nEláha d-Meir!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nמַלְּפָנָא דִבְרוּרְיָא<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nTeacher of Bruriah!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Pesachim 62b&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nMalfana di-Vrurya!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nבִּזְכוּתֵיהּ דְבַר יוֹחַאי<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nIn Bar Yochai’s merit!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[12]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Zohar 3 144a&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nBi-zkhuteih d-var Yoḥai!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nבִּיקָרַהּ דְּיַלְתָּא<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nIn Yalta’s honor!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[13]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> See Berakhot 51b.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nBi-ykareih d-Yalta!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nאֱלֹהֵי הַמֶּרְכָּבָה<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nGod of the chariot!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nElohei ha-merkavah!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nעֶזְרַת הַשְׁבָטִים<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nHelper of the tribes!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nEzrat ha-sh’vatim!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nעֲנֵֽנוּ!<br />\nרָחוּם וְחָנוּן<br />\nעֲנֵֽנוּ\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAnswer us,<br />\nMerciful and compassionate!<br />\nAnswer us!\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"romanized-transliteration\" lang=\"heb-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nAneinu,<br />\nRaḥum v-ḥanun!<br />\nAneinu!\n</div>\